{"tid":991041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重罰?] 兩周第二宗！瞞擁私樓 判囚1個月緩刑罰$5,000","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:38:40.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e41c6647601bf5342f5b0c7fa2f3d420e7cc8a52","tid":991041,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"1名黃大仙富山邨公屋居民，去年5月填寫入息及資產申報表時，隱瞞當時以聯權共有方式，擁有1個西營盤住宅物業，沒有申報，昨日（21日）在九龍城裁判法院，被裁定虛假陳述罪成，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">判罰5,000元及監禁1個月，緩刑18個月</span></strong>，是兩周內第二宗同類罪成個案。房屋署指，會向有關住戶追回因資料不正確而少付的租金，而根據新修訂「富戶政策」，若公屋住戶擁有香港住宅物業，不論其家庭入息或資產水平為何，均須遷離他們現居的公屋單位。<br />\n<br />\n房屋署又指，住戶須準確填寫入息及資產申報表，仔細閱讀表格內容及填表須知，並按指定方法，計算和填寫其收入及資產。若涉虛假陳述，最高可罰款5萬元及監禁6個月；若忽略提供入息及資產申報表指明的詳情，最高可罰款2.5萬元及監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190122/59170638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59170638&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=75c9cdf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59170638&h=ca78ac70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190122/59170638</a>"},{"pid":"027d51f932e1708fc02e922caf4d2a19cbc93576","tid":991041,"uid":7369,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"屌, 博得過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80c38a2484ba771110c4b740f7f97126b614e96","tid":991041,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"本土check得到就告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4fb1a53d36830ea9ea3e9b701ab82a62faa4ae","tid":991041,"uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":0,